&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bajaj General Insurance.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bajaj General Insurance Limited has introduced &amp;lsquo;Eco Assure&amp;rsquo;, an innovative add-on cover specifically designed for commercial vehicle owners.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Depreciation Waiver:&lt;/strong&gt; The policy provides a &lt;strong&gt;100% waiver&lt;/strong&gt; on depreciation if reconditioned parts are used and a &lt;strong&gt;25% waiver&lt;/strong&gt; for new parts.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Relief:&lt;/strong&gt; It eliminates the &lt;strong&gt;Compulsory Deductible&lt;/strong&gt; during claims, reducing the immediate out-of-pocket expenses for vehicle operators.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plan Variants:&lt;/strong&gt; It offers two versions: &lt;strong&gt;Eco Assure Essential&lt;/strong&gt; (basic repairs, towing) and &lt;strong&gt;Eco Assure Advantage&lt;/strong&gt; (legal costs, electric/hybrid system cover).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coverage:&lt;/strong&gt; Includes 100% protection for paintwork and external body parts like bumpers, bonnets, and lamps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Add-on Cover&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;An add-on is an extra protection layer that can be purchased over a standard comprehensive insurance policy to cover specific risks not included in the base plan.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Compulsory Deductible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;This is the fixed amount a policyholder must pay before the insurance company covers the rest of the claim. Eco Assure helps waive this for commercial operators.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;K. V. Ramana Murty.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kompella Venkata Ramana Murty (K. V. Ramana Murty) has been appointed as a Whole-Time Member of the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Service Background:&lt;/strong&gt; He is a retired 1991-batch IDAS officer who previously served as the Additional Controller General of Defence Accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tenure:&lt;/strong&gt; His appointment is for a period of &lt;strong&gt;three years&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vacancy:&lt;/strong&gt; He succeeds &lt;strong&gt;Ananth Narayan G&lt;/strong&gt;, whose term concluded in October 2025.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SEBI Board:&lt;/strong&gt; The board now includes four WTMs: K. V. Ramana Murty, Amarjeet Singh, Kamlesh Chandra Varshney, and Sandip Pradhan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;SEBI Whole-Time Members&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;WTMs are functional heads of various departments within SEBI and play a critical role in decision-making and market regulation alongside the Chairperson.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Composition&lt;/strong&gt;: The board is led by a Chairperson and includes 4 Whole-Time Members and 4 Part-Time Members.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
